&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;THE LEEDS TEACHING HOSPITALS NHS TRUST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Trust Doctor in Thoracic Surgery (Registrar Level)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;SJUH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Leeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust is seeking to appoint a Trust Doctor within the department of Thoracic Surgery. The post will be based at St James’s University Hospital within the Oncology Clinical Services Unit.   &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will be expected to engage in the care of patients both pre and post operatively, attending relevant MDT’s, attending theatre and clinic sessions, being involved in the on call rota and teaching of medical students.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Candidates must be fully registered with the General Medical Council or be eligible for registration at the time of application and hold a license to practice. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note the closing date for these posts may be subject to change depending on the response received.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further details, please refer to the job description and person specification.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interested candidates should contact:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Mr Kostas Papagiannopoulos, Thoracic Surgeon via his secretary on 0113 2068776 or email &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;k.papagiannopoulos@nhs.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
